{
  "id": "RAW_e5d9039b",
  "title": "AI 效果涌现！一文读懂百度世界 2025",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5NzUyMzM1Mg==&mid=2247661935&idx=2&sn=9154cb7cec5289374f16187762095a2d",
  "date": "2025-11-13 09:12:00",
  "author": "百度AI",
  "siteName": "百度AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 8px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">▎怎么让每一家企业、每一个人都能“内化 AI 能力”？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，百度世界2025在北京·国家会议中心举办。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">百度创始人李彦宏在演讲时表示，“我们更关心如何让 AI 跟我们要做的每一项任务，都能够进行有机的结合，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">让 AI 成为企业发展和个人成长的原生推动力。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">他指出，当 AI 能力被内化，成为一种原生的能力，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能就不再是成本，而是生产力。</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;\">\n     <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 2px 2px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100178278\" data-ratio=\"0.6666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e92f4073&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FTQX7ER5HdB1b53QoFASmrpOyuqxGH7fN61YsanAOZDTMc903ZqpqsJQ3iaTZZ7fAuHsVCY2DDzWCz9KlozDjHcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">百度正全面内化 AI 能力，用 AI 重构业务</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。以搜索为例，这是百度第一个进行重构的产品，也是全球范围里，AI 化改造最激进的搜索引擎——百度搜索，现已从文字内容和链接为主的互联网应用，转型成以富媒体内容为主的 AI 应用。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">大会上，李彦宏再次强调 AI 应用创新的价值，他表示，AI 产业结构正从不健康的“正金字塔”，转变为健康的“倒金字塔”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:25px 15px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在不健康的“正金字塔”结构上，位于底层的芯片获取最大价值，而模型、AI 应用价值则向上逐层递减；</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“倒金字塔”中，模型产生10倍于芯片的价值，AI 应用则能创造100倍价值，从而形成健康的 AI 产业结构。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;\">\n     <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 2px 2px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100178276\" data-ratio=\"0.6666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=478bb872&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FTQX7ER5HdB1b53QoFASmrpOyuqxGH7fNdmOczV3IZatok6fdiblfibJIzJX9k4iae4YM56hAVYzzjwzjELicXficz2w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“过去一年，我们看到模型能力逐步走出了聊天机器人的范畴，我们看到数字人技术，代码智能体技术，甚至是通用场景的能够自主演化、寻找全局最优解的智能体技术，都有了长足的发展。”李彦宏表示。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">会上，百度发布新一代“实时互动型数字人”；宣布秒哒升级至2.0，已生成超40万应用；同时，还带来全球首个自我演化的智能体“伐谋”，能为交通、能源、金融等应用场景找到最优解。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们正在跨越一个全新临界点，</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从‘智能涌现’走向‘效果涌现’。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”李彦宏说。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;\">\n     <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 3px 3px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100178280\" data-ratio=\"1.8518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fa84ca72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FTQX7ER5HdB1b53QoFASmrpOyuqxGH7fNoniagNH2dhTXh84sAGN0fsKJvM9JckqyquLnWoEVWWJHWsM46joItqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当天，还有诸多 AI 成果集中亮相——</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">文心大模型5.0正式发布，在全模态理解、创意写作、智能体规划、指令遵循等方面表现出色；</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">萝卜快跑每周全无人订单超25万，全球出行服务次数超1700万，全球第一；</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">发布新一代昆仑芯和超节点产品天池；</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">GenFlow 升级至3.0，成全球最大通用智能体。</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，萝卜快跑、慧播星数字人技术、秒哒、文库网盘等一系列产品，将全面加速出海。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform-origin: center center;-webkit-transform-origin: center center;-moz-transform-origin: center center;-o-transform-origin: center center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;智能生活 AI 效果涌现&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 8px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">▎发布“实时互动型”数字人</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">向全球开放慧播星数字人技术</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，数字人技术实现了重大飞跃。作为 AI 时代的一种全新的、通用的交互界面，数字人让 AI 拥有了人的“面孔”，让人机交互变得像和真人对话一样自然。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;\">\n     <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 2px 2px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100178277\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=64033fcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FTQX7ER5HdB1b53QoFASmrpOyuqxGH7fNMXlo6Uu6TTxCTHHQ9VONa96sQuGFMkibGicfia8zlicnuJIZm5fxklHngQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">李彦宏指出，数字人是一个多模态的、全新的产品形态，具有非常大的应用前景。今年双十一，83%的开播主播都使用过数字人，开播直播间数同比增长了119%，GMV 同比提升91%。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">会上，百度发布新一代“实时互动型数字人”，具备实时响应、声情并茂、明察善断的特质，互动性进一步增强。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果演讲者在台上演示时，手机突然断网了怎么办？”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在互动连麦环节，面对产品经理即兴发挥的问题，罗永浩数字人不仅表情、声音、动作像真人一样鲜活自然，还给了出完美回复——做好两手准备，真诚讲述产品理念和故事，“说白了，技术故障不可怕，可怕的是没预案，还愣在那儿，那才叫真尴尬。”</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">现场，李彦宏宣布，慧播星数字人技术面向全球开放。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 8px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">▎</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">百度搜索</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">富媒体覆盖率达70%</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们用 AI 重构搜索结果页，这不是简单地在搜索结果中插入个 AI 摘要，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">而是把搜索从一个以文字内容和链接为主的互联网应用，</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">转化为一个以图片视频等富媒体内容为主的 AI 应用。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">”李彦宏表示，百度是全球所有搜索引擎当中 AI 化改造最激进的。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width: 100%;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"line-height: 0;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;\">\n     <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(160, 160, 160) 2px 2px 5px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100178283\" data-ratio=\"0.6666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5bfc93d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FTQX7ER5HdB1b53QoFASmrpOyuqxGH7fNE7QfPURxpXul9U9wSO1nu38QHX8nY1v7DTInhadeHIBicO87lhQ856A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，绝大部分的搜索结果都是由 AI 生成的，首条结果的富媒体化覆盖率已达70%。这意味着，10个问题中有7个的答案，不再是一条条链接，而是一个图片、一个视频、一个直播，甚至是一个数字人。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:25px 15px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在用户提出小众问题，如“科学家是怎么判断一个动物相当于人类几岁智商的？”时，AI 搜索能够专门为此生成视频答案，比文字回答更生动，还能降低理解门槛。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅如此，百度搜索还完成了从“找信息”到“完成任务”的蜕变。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:25px 15px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:100%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding:0px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，当用户拍照咨询药品信息时，百度搜索可以一站式完成识别药品、生成用药计划、定时推送用药提醒的全流程。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前，百度正通过 AI API 向全球开放 AI 搜索能力，三星、荣耀、vivo 等625家厂商，都已接入搜索 API。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(25, 110, 213);line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1px;padding: 0px 8px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">▎</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">进化+出海！</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒哒2.0上线</span></strong></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">会上，百度无代码开发工具“秒哒”，宣布进化至2.0，具备两大特点——</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">全栈应用，一键生成：</span></span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户可通过秒哒，一句话完成从开发、调试、部署、到线上托管的全流程操作，直接生成一个前端交互、后端存储、工具插件的“活应用”；</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 40px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(25, 110, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一站式开发与分发：</span></span></strong><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户通过秒哒生成的应用，可以一键发布到公网，既能享受百度搜索的亿级流量曝光，也支持发布成微信小程序。</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">大会现场，秒哒2.0在十分钟内就生成了一个闲置服装电商平台，除了基础的选购、付款功能，还加载了“AI 试装”插件，只需要选购衣服、上传个人照片，即可快速收到 AI 生成的上身效果。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"